    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Lords of the Fallen》</strong> 在相互连通的广袤世界中讲述了一段全新史诗角色扮演冒险之旅。 <br><br>漫长的时光过去，被人类击败的邪神阿迪尔即将卷土重来。化身为神话中的黑暗远征军，在这段宏大的角色扮演体验中，让阿迪尔永世不得超生。在两个平行国度中穿梭冒险，与庞大首领进行殊死战、面对瞬息万变的战斗，并沉浸在深刻的故事之中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras/9d394b7b3410a8af816de79f92814ac1.avif?t=1771236480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras_big/9d394b7b3410a8af816de79f92814ac1.avif?t=1771236480 width=1560 height=584 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索相互连通的广袤世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿行于两个广阔的平行世界之间。生者的国度和亡者的世界中都有各自不同的道路、秘密、宝藏和敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras/c75eafea4af0bc528efcb385e02460fe.avif?t=1771236480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras_big/c75eafea4af0bc528efcb385e02460fe.avif?t=1771236480 width=1560 height=584 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握颇具挑战性的高速战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在超过百余种凶猛兵器中做出选择，从重型连枷到速射弩一应俱全，也可以施展奥秘之力发动毁灭性的魔法攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras/8353a7d6d7e2d9ffd3f5ffaf9ba31ec0.avif?t=1771236480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras_big/8353a7d6d7e2d9ffd3f5ffaf9ba31ec0.avif?t=1771236480 width=1560 height=584 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >书写你的传奇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义设置你的角色外观，然后就可以在 9 种不同的角色职业中选择一个。无论选择哪一条起始路径，都可以通过升级属性和武器来贯彻自己的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras/0da9d7d662df88c0d220edbfad62478a.avif?t=1771236480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras_big/0da9d7d662df88c0d220edbfad62478a.avif?t=1771236480 width=1560 height=584 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参与在线多人模式，团结一心</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自体验单人战役，或在在线合作模式与其他玩家齐心奋战。你可以随时与他人同行，无论是休闲模式或“共享进度”模式，双方玩家都会储存所有进度。此外，使用“免费好友通行证”可以邀请任何人加入游戏，即使对方未拥有本游戏也不例外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras/340689fede5c56267bb077788d91c410.avif?t=1771236480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501750/extras_big/340689fede5c56267bb077788d91c410.avif?t=1771236480 width=1560 height=584 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >70 余次发行后更新</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 余次的发行后更新包括大受好评的 2.0 版，我们透过完全重制的战斗系统和显著的效能强化大幅改善体验、对众多新任务线和模式的难度平衡进行严谨调整，并新增大量提升游玩舒适度功能。</p>",
